                  </hi>. I sent my portmanteau by the Parcels Delivery Company—this is it—(<hi rend="italic">looking at it</hi>)—it contains the articles stated, which are mine—it has my direction on it in my own writing.</p>
               <p>(Solomon Hyams, a fishmonger, of Middlesex-street, Whitechapel; and John Moseley, a confectioner, of Goodman's-yard; gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
